     A port of <a href="https://github.com/sainnhe/gruvbox-material">sainnhe/gruvbox-material</a> to Intellij IDE's. Using <a href="https://github.com/subtheme-dev/monokai-pro">subtheme-dev/monokai-pro</a> as the base with some modifications

